kano-peripherals (3.11.0-0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Add support for poweroff on boot if battery is low
  * Refactored DBus services architecture with DeviceDiscovery
  * Added support for board hotplugging live
  * Supporting board hotplugging in CPU monitor animation
  * Added support for LED Speaker back
  * Various fixes to library controlling PiHat and PowerHat
  * Systemd unit file to turn off PiHat and LED Speaker lights

 -- Team Kano <dev@kano.me>  Mon, 17 May 2017 17:56:45 +0100

